297
00:13:45,390 --> 00:13:47,080
It's not too late to know it now.

298
00:13:47,080 --> 00:13:47,590
He…

299
00:13:47,590 --> 00:13:48,710
All right.

300
00:13:48,710 --> 00:13:50,190
Have a seat.

301
00:13:50,190 --> 00:13:52,390
-Xixi. Tell him to sit.
-Sit over there.

302
00:13:57,870 --> 00:13:58,470
